textBox.richText: Saturday saw #3 in Max’s mogul series...he took 7th. Alli had picked up the Sled passes, so right after that, we headed for the cirque...jumped into Cornice Canyon. Sunday started off with a lap through Destiny and Waterfall with Alli and Max; they went off early for lunch, and I pulled another lap through the west headwall...and then met up with Gunter for one more lap...this time through the south headwall.
